txt.en: All your efforts to aid in the sustenance of Mûr Ghala earns you a deeper relationship as a friend to the Kintai Elves of Sul Madásh.
You continue to prove your value, honesty, and measured assistance to the Kintai Elves of Sul Madásh.
Friend of the Kintai of Sul Madásh
You must earn Friend standing with the Kintai of Sul Madásh
